      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm looking at our Q3 reports for the electronics warehouse and the shrinkage numbers are way higher than usual. can you help me figure out how to factor this increased shrinkage into our inventory turnover ratio calculation? i need to see how much it's actually dragging down our efficiency.",
